### Issue description

#### Add Button in designer, => set darkmode at program , then run => got the issue with darkmode

use Darkmode does not apply darkmode correctly  for `button` , `dateTimePicker` and `monthCalendar`  and maybe other controls (not test).  

Control add in runtime has the same issue

<img width="815" height="483" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a5d3a821-0330-4ce3-8929-f16e5ee3c730" />

